        "contentType": "VIDEO",
        "title": "Top takeaways from Trump's address on Iran war, Strait of Hormuz",
        "description": "<p>President Trump declared that the Iran war may be far from over as the US leader vowed to <a target=\"_blank\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/economy/policy/article/trump-declares-other-countries-need-to-take-the-lead-on-the-strait-of-hormuz-in-national-address-161325048.html\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\">bomb the country \"back to the Stone Age\"</a>  in his national address on Wednesday.</p><p>US stocks (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI?p=%5EDJI&.tsrc=fin-srch\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\">^DJI</a>, <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC?p=%5EIXIC&.tsrc=fin-srch\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\">^IXIC</a>, <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC?p=%5EGSPC&.tsrc=fin-srch\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\">^GSPC</a>) have slowed their rally in Thursday's session, while oil prices (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F/\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\">CL=F</a>, <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/BZ=F/\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\">BZ=F</a>) have surged.</p><p>Yahoo Finance Washington Correspondent Ben Werschkul reacts to Trump's latest stance on the escalating conflicts in the Middle East, reopening <a target=\"_blank\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/trump-claims-us-is-totally-independent-of-the-middle-east-hes-overlooking-how-global-energy-markets-work-100000997.html\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\">the Strait of Hormuz</a>, and how global energy markets are subsequently responding.</p>",
        "summary": "President Trump declared that the Iran war may be far from over as the US leader vowed to bomb the country \"back to the Stone Age\" in his national address on Wednesday.US stocks (^DJI, ^IXIC, ^GSPC) have slowed their rally in Thursday's session, while oil prices (CL=F, BZ=F) have surged.Yahoo Finance Washington Correspondent Ben Werschkul reacts to Trump's latest stance on the escalating conflicts in the Middle East, reopening the Strait of Hormuz, and how global energy markets are subsequently responding.",
